2014-01-07  Simon 'human/sf-mensch' Sobisch <sf-mensch@users.sf.net> 

   * typeck.c : Bugfix: no exception check for NULL address on FREE statement
       (as this is explicit allowed)

2012-10-24  Sergey Kashyrin <ska@kiska.net>

   * tree.c : Fix incorrect counting of number of digits for "$", "+", and "-"
       almost as per Ron Norman (bug #39).

2012-10-24  Sergey Kashyrin <ska@kiska.net>

   * pplex.l : Lexer was missing comment lines in FREE format, i.e.
       trying to process "* COPY 12345." and look for "12345" file as a copybook :-)

2012-07-24  Simon 'human/sf-mensch' Sobisch <sf-mensch@users.sf.net> 

   * field.c : Added check for maximum size of group items

2012-06-20  Sergey Kashyrin <ska@kiska.net>

   * cobc.c : Retrofit fixes - Added -A and -Q options (I had those as -Wc,
       and -Wl, but it went as -A and -Q in later version, so let use those)
   * typeck.c : Retrofit fixes - NULL pointer crash correction,
       CB_USAGE_DISPLAY generation correction
   * codegen.c : Retrofit fixes - initialize_type corrected to handle
       occurs at 01 level, output_initialize_compound corrected,
       output_perform_exit - OSVS corrected
   * parser.y : Retrofit fixes - exclude level 77 from "Item requires a
       data name" check

2012-05-09  Simon 'human/sf-mensch' Sobisch <sf-mensch@users.sf.net> 

   * cobc.c : Added conversion for enabling options in WIN style

